@node History

   2.1   17-12-96 - Added abilty to save the list of Factors
                    Added Settings/MUI... menu
                    Now user must enter a number between 2 and 2147483647 (2^32 - 1)

   2.0   11-12-96 - Second aminet release - NOW WITH GUI!

                    Added an @{"MUI" link mui} GUI - my first ever :)
                    Made argument passing the Amiga 2.0+ standard, ie,
                    passing ? brings up a template.

   1.0   05-12-96 - First aminet release

@endnode

